examples.en: He tapped me on the shoulder.
I think our phone is being tapped.
She tapped her feet in time to the music.
I went up and tapped on the window.
He flinched when I tapped him on the shoulder.
She tapped ash from her cigarette.
Murray's phone calls to Australia were tapped.
She tapped timidly on the door.
He tapped his security code into the computer.
He was tapped for an exclusive Senior Society.
He tapped in the code and the lock disengaged.
He whistled the tune and tapped out the rhythm.
He turned as someone tapped him on the shoulder.
We hope that additional sources of funding can be tapped.
Mr. Calthorpe tapped the points of the fingers of each hand together.
